Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:25.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}絢爛奪目 不堪直視
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:31.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}初始不期而至 迅如暴風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:35.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被你的眸 深深吸入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:41.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}初感的衝動 因為你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:46.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想窺探 想知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:55.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}未知的你 真實的心請允許我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:58.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}數著星星的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:00.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你與我邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:03.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}兒時仰望天際
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虔誠祈禱的我已翱翔在天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.30,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}胸中栽培夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思念孕育力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:13.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}願與你攜手去往無限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:17.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}成為導航未來之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Montero的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是你們欠考慮我才安排的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是貝魯利救了那女人的命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可能還幫了這個女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,今天晚上辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,明天麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,到調查部走一次好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有勞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不光是這女的 那東西也是調查部…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,說幾遍才明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這種待遇 明顯違反了國際法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是否認隸屬亞美利亞軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那就談不上違反
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,據我所知那背包是亞美利亞軍產的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有商標嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,既然Capital軍對它一籌莫展
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,今後就由調查部負責
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是組建Capital軍的幕後黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,貝克上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這位學生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我提到過的盧因·李候補生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說是個昆達拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有這麼髒麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼說話所以討人厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,躲開的同時還防禦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是棵好苗子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝賞識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是 謝謝您送的shank
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,諾蕾朵回家睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,法皇大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我會讓他們保證Capital塔的正常運營
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那自然好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是諾蕾朵·納古小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是 大人晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你又去動海盜的機動戰士了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,專門監視外國違禁情況的調查部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,找宇宙海盜什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,聖芙蘭學園後援團的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,諾蕾朵·納古小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,母親能想法帶她回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把俘虜？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯 對她一見鍾情了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一見鍾情 一見鍾情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哈羅比…諾蕾朵小姐的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它叫諾貝魯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,本打算貝魯利加入Capital衛隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,送給他做禮物…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利也能駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,母親和調查部的昆珀上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這隻手 是不是出過血了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,小心發炎 來人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,又要出擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,卡希爾上尉剛戰死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,多半是去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這架Montero去送死？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,中…中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,您剛從本土回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,現在出擊太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,卡希爾上尉他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因為我不在時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,去營救艾達殿下才功敗垂成的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,請退後 小心摔下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,區區Capital軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不過是群剛組建的新兵蛋子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒能制止他 也有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這次不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍不會想到這個時間點上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,會有二次攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有機可乘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,被捧成天才 有點得意忘形了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔 正被宇宙的事分心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以機不可失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先聽聽蘇爾坎總監的報告！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,也得先救出艾達殿下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你的光束長矛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,連接宇宙的臍帶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不久前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,連靠近那裏都觸犯禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,卡希爾上尉卻因為掛念艾達殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,冒險潛入那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,成熟男人感情用事！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好漫長的編隊訓練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嘻嘻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,拿你沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,女海盜比貝魯利還大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我是惦記機動戰士和昆珀上校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天晚上 被那女的揪住衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,覺得她說得有理了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,見那女的被抓走 喜歡上她了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大清早幹嘛的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫貝魯利·塞納姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,上校喊我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是那個候補生貝魯利？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚 她什麼來歷？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:08:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅·曼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,來 別怕 別怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,獨自一人時 她時常會那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,關於宇宙海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有證據表明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他們是亞美利亞軍旗下的獨立部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,機體的宇宙背包上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,還發現了亞美利亞國內生產商的商標與刻印
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利·塞納姆前來接受詢問
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,再降低高度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,會有點顛簸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼 這也是調查部的工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,還是昨晚的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這和軍隊有什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,想到就做不管時間是嗎 貝魯利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那架機動戰士的面板上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,儘是些我沒見過的商標
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她說了些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有些事不用拷問 也會得到相同的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯看上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,諾蕾朵！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一見鍾情？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一見鍾情 鍾情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,上校閣下的意見是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,上校是位紳士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不必操心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我對貝魯利為什麼能駕駛G-Self…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅·曼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,諾蕾朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍進入迎戰狀態？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,法皇有何指示？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,早禮拜的時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要求釋放你們逮捕的海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,並返還其駕駛的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果拒絕 就破壞Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,以上是最後通牒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,散佈米諾夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,會合坐標 明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Montero 脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,喝完倒頭就睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你說我殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也有不少人身負重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔附近 究竟遭受多大損失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,卡希爾上尉他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,卡希爾上尉他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一直想阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔繼續獨佔能源
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,之所以由SCord教配給光子電池
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是為了避免人類重蹈宇宙世紀的覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,能源和工具 只要遵守道德善加利用…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因為做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,人類才差點在宇宙世紀死光的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,卡希爾上尉他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,看來他是位…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,能成為救世主的人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有…這麼極端
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我認同你關於善用工具的主張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才想問二位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐和貝魯利成功駕駛了G-Self
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,還有拉萊雅·曼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:13:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這位少女是Capital衛隊週一在空中逮捕的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,警報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,空襲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,警報？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,散佈米諾夫斯基粒子前？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要求我們返還人質？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,走到底對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,又是來接你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,同伴不只上尉一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,上校說 三樓可以去駕駛艙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是在試探我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,上校是調查部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,幕布為什麼掛在這種地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有能用的Catsith嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是演習 快給我出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,還有空在這種事上浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直連Capital衛隊都不如！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚空襲 趕上籌備建軍典禮…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,把能動的Catsith和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,FRag統統拖出機庫 馬上！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,上校在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,軍港有宇宙用的背包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,調查部的一貫風格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是從哪裏搞來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊從哪裏呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是Capital塔的回應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,雷達都歇菜了 還這樣摸過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是傳說中的Recksnow麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Recten的改造機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒見識過戰爭的人的想法真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是回應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,妨礙我工作的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就做好掛綵的準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,雷哈頓碼 確認
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才是什麼反應？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？是啟動系統
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,克裏姆·尼科是個想利用我的青年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利·塞納姆 檢查臉部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？ 好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 眼睛亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,德蘭森上尉 沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼用什麼了 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,起飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,叢林裏用氣墊太勉強了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不會受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼動了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,開動會被誤會的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼誤會的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是駕駛自己的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,返回自己的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,誒…快動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,軍隊已經出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,放手 我要回家！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那東西從來沒人能開動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,上面有四個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 韋米特運營長官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,法皇大人的意思是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self正在被奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,聲音再輕點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看得見前面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:17:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是克裏姆·尼科
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,被打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Catsith被…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Montero的 長矛光束索的性能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不能讓他們在Capital塔交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 號稱軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不過是Capital衛隊出身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是天才！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續拉升
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只裝近戰武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,起飛 升空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,雷哈頓碼 確認
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,該死的蒼蠅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,長矛 是這麼用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼長矛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那機體是昨天晚上的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是凱爾貝斯先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有滅火劑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是貝魯利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我在駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,誰在駕駛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放下起落架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,輪子輪子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快減速
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,凱爾貝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,貝…貝魯利·塞納姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.99,0:20:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利候補生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下 艾達殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,克裏姆·尼科前來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下 為什麼阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那種不著邊際的攻擊 沒有威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,回遠古巨獸號 克裏姆·尼科
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？你說回哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 運營長官
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是 敵人撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是逃跑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對膽大妄為的亞美利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,必須中斷光子電池供應 以作為懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,能理解您作為運營長官的立場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,記得我說有四個人坐進了G-Self嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 女俘虜和監視中的拉萊雅·曼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,還有諾蕾朵·納古…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,誒 還有我家的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有傷到一根Capital塔的纜繩是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那裏將來會成為亞美利亞軍的宇宙基地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙基地？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,異想天開的青年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,身為總統兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,卻對機動戰士情有獨鍾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下身後的少女可以駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這個少年也有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,臭小子 他敢…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這音樂怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是設計師的嗜好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,今天好的話明天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.77,0:22:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,明天好的話後天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.68,0:24:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然知道艾達小姐的心情複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我又何嘗不是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.73,0:24:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在敵人的軍艦上被要求駕駛G-Self給他們看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.12,0:24:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,被要求和盛氣凌人的中尉一起迎戰Capital軍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.09,0:24:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.53,0:24:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 G之復國
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.23,0:24:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Catsith亂舞
